Table 5 presents the numbers/proportions of truly and falsely validated significant CpG sites. The three improved joint score tests have higher true validation ratios than joint LRT, KS test, and AW test. Among all the tests, iAW.Lev had the highest true validation rate (89.2%) and lowest false validation rate (10.8%), followed by iAW.TM and iAW.BF. And we also applied the 6 joint tests on the adjusted data sets, the performances of them are similar (see Additional file 1: Table S1).
